All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
AnswerBox
AnswerBoxes are designed to be wide rectangles that contain some text.
AnswerBoxMovable
These AnswerBoxes can be moved by dragging them.
AudioPlayer
AudioPlayer class is used to play different audios in the game
ChoiceScreen
ChoiceScreen is the Screen type used for most of the game.
FeelingMeter
FeelingMeter class is used to keep track of story emotional states FeelingMeter class keeps track of emotional states in the story.
GlobalElements
The GlobalElements group hold all elements needed in all screens of the game.
MainGame
The MainGame class runs the game.
MainMenuScreen
The MainMenuScreen class is a screen shown as the main menu.
MySkin
The MySkin class holds all textures, fonts and UI styles for the game.
SaveHandler
The SaveHandler class handles the saving, loading and resetting of the game.
Screen
Screen is an abstract class that is used to create different screen layouts for the game.
Utility
The Utility class contains various methods that are used by various other classes.
